 shows our test. It seems unclear because it mentions a class. I’ll check to see if the test report includes our specific test. It’s important for us to confirm that everything aligns correctly; otherwise, we might draw the wrong conclusions. I want to make sure I’m on top of this so I can provide accurate information!\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_gnBgL8AlQ0DuBeuJWRf8gUEp|fc_0d9a5266f308cffb0169f498dc8d388193a231b966ea4b3624", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "ls tests/src/org.freemarker/freemarker/2.3.31/build/test-results/test/TEST-fm.FreemarkerDebugImplRmiDebuggedEnvironmentImplStubTest.xml 2>/dev/null && grep -n \"FreemarkerDebugImplRmiDebugged\" tests/src/org.freemarker/freemarker/2.3.31/build/reports/tests/test/index.html || true"}, "partialJson": "{\"command\":\"ls tests/src/org.freemarker/freemarker/2.3.31/build/test-results/test/TEST-fm.FreemarkerDebugImplRmiDebuggedEnvironmentImplStubTest.xml 2>/dev/null && grep -n \\\"FreemarkerDebugImplRmiDebugged\\\" tests/src/org.freemarker/freemarker/2.3.31/build/reports/tests/test/index.html || true\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2356, "output": 1166, "cacheRead": 68096, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 71618, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777637574860, "responseId": "resp_0d9a5266f308cffb0169f498c76c6c81938e5a894cf3302b54"}}
